<xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" n="sb;3;6991" targOrder="U" to="DITTO" type="reprint from">SB3,6991;PEdg108</xref></head><div lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="edition"><div n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Ζήνων Κρότωι χαίρειν. ὡς ἂν τάχιστα λάβηις τὴν ἐπιστολήν, 


    <lb n="2"/>λαβὲ παρὰ Πάσιτος τοῦ Ἰουδαίου ἐρίων <expan>μν<ex cert="high">ᾶς</ex></expan> <num value="25">κε</num> καὶ ἀπέγδος Ἀρτεμι-

    <lb n="3"/>δώρωι ἵνα κατασκευάσηι στρωμάτιον, ὥστε τῶι μήκει ἐπὶ δίεδρον 

    <lb n="4"/>ἢ μικρῶι μεῖζον, διπρόσωπον· χρεία γὰρ αὐτοῦ ἐστιν ὥστε Πισικλεῖ· 

    <lb n="5"/>καὶ ὡς ἂν τάχιστα γένηται, ἀπόστειλον εἰς Μέμφιν πρὸς Ἀρτεμί-

    <lb n="6"/>δωρον, καὶ πειράθητι ὅπως ἐν <expan>ἡμ<ex cert="high">έραις</ex></expan> <num value="15">ιε</num> γένηται. γεγράφαμεν δὲ 

    <lb n="7"/>καὶ Πάσι δοῦναί σοι τὰ ἔρια. 

    <lb n="8"/>ἔρρωσο. <expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="33">λγ</num>, Ἐπεὶφ <num value="28">κη</num>. 
</ab></div><div n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="9"/>Κρότωι. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.886" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.886" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="-253" notBefore="-253" type="textDate" value="-0253-09-17">17. Sept. 253 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.886" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Cair. Zen.</title><biblScope type="volume">2</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">59241</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">886</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="DDbDP"><series>0092</series>; <biblScope type="volume">2</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">59241</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0092;2;59241" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.886" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">78</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">IX</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">52</biblScope></bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.886" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl default="NO" type="illustration">Pl. XVII (Rekto)</bibl><bibl default="NO" type="illustration">Seider, Paläographie III, 1, II Abb. 36 a, S. 204 und II Abb. 36, S. 205 und S. 315, 4</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.886" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikationen</head><listBibl default="NO"><b